Title: Meghan and Harry interview: Royal Family 'very much not racist' - William
Content: The Duke of Cambridge says he has yet to speak to his brother Prince Harry following the Oprah interview.

Title: Thor the lion has a vasectomy in Dutch zoo
Content: The big cat fathered five cubs last year, and the zoo now says it has enough of his DNA.

Title: Pentagon rebukes Fox host Tucker Carlson for mocking female troops
Content: Fox News host Tucker Carlson had called female service members "a mockery of the US military".

Title: Running from terror in Mozambique
Content: A militant Islamist insurgency in north-east Mozambique has forced half a million people to flee for fear of beheadings and abductions.

Title: Twins peak with more born than ever before
Content: One in every 42 children is born a twin and much has changed over the past 30 years, a report finds.

Title: Covid pandemic: Biden to order all US adults be eligible for vaccine
Content: The president is set to announce the move during a speech on Thursday evening.

Title: A bowling alley like you've never seen it before
Content: A one-shot drone tour of a Minneapolis establishment has been celebrated for its production genius.

Title: De Blasio: NYC mayor calls on Cuomo to quit over harassment claims
Content: Andrew Cuomo has been accused of sexual misconduct by six women, allegations he denies.

Title: Uber and Lyft to swap data on banned drivers
Content: The two taxi apps have faced scrutiny for how they handle incidents of sexual assault and other safety issues.

Title: Oxford-AstraZeneca: Denmark suspends vaccine 'as a precaution'
Content: The decision follows a death and reports of blood clots, but the health minister says no link is established.
